page.title: 08Traffic in Great Shelford
page.content:
On the main road, over one hour there were : 408 (7/min) cars going into Great Shelford 348 (6/min) cars going out of Great Shelford (at the main intersection)
This was taken at about four o'clock and may have been due to children returning from school. On a secondary road we also counted the traffic over a one hour period :
204 (3/min) cars going into Great Shelford 252 (4/min) cars going out of Great Shelford
This was taken at about five o'clock, in the middle of the rush hour.
